      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON KINNIE (1) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 6 lengths into second (22.33) at this track in a Grade 4 over 380m. Can measure up this time. TIME PASSAGES (6) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (22.31) in a Mix 5 at this track. Has a good record here including six wins. Expected to run well. ON REPORT (2) was a course and distance winner (29.14) last time also from the same draw, scoring by 2.75 lengths in a P5. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. SLIM NIKITA (8) profiles nicely here at this trip.",
